PN,41601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774054967
OL,3,CFamily of teenager who died after
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak call for better
OL,5,Cprotection
OL,7,FThe father of an 18-year-old girl who
OL,8,Fdied following an outbreak of
OL,9,Fmeningitis in Kent said his family's
OL,10,Fdevastation is "immeasurable" as he
OL,11,Fcalled for better protection for young
OL,12,Fpeople.
OL,14,FJuliette Kenny died on Saturday March
OL,15,F14, one day after first showing
OL,16,Fsymptoms which were vomiting and
OL,17,Fdiscolouration in her cheeks, her
OL,18,Ffather Michael Kenny said.
OL,26,@rD@POUrD@]O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774054967
OL,3,CFamily of teenager who died after
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak call for better
OL,5,Cprotection
OL,7,FMr Kenny said his daughter had been
OL,8,F"fit, healthy and strong" before her
OL,9,Fdeath and had completed the practical
OL,10,Fassessment for her PE A-level on
OL,11,FThursday March 12.
OL,13,FJuliette, who was described by her
OL,14,Ffather as having a "beautifully
OL,15,Fpositive energy", is one of two
OL,16,Fstudents who have died following the
OL,17,Foutbreak of meningitis B in the county.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@YO]vD@TOUwD@PO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774054967
OL,3,CFamily of teenager who died after
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak call for better
OL,5,Cprotection
OL,7,FMr Kenny said "no family should
OL,8,Fexperience this pain and tragedy" and
OL,9,Fthat "this can be avoided", adding
OL,10,Fthat he wanted his daughter's legacy
OL,11,Fto be "lasting change".
OL,13,FIt comes as more than 100 students in
OL,14,FKent were turned away while trying to
OL,15,Fget a meningitis vaccine after
OL,16,Fofficials closed the queue on Thursday.
OL,18,FIn a statement to the Press
OL,19,FAssociation, Mr Kenny said: "We are
OL,20,Fincredibly proud parents to two
OL,21,Fwonderful daughters.
OL,26,@oD@OOUpD@aO]qD@FOUqD@ZO]sD@GOUsD@VO]{D@
OL,26,A]OU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774054967
OL,3,CFamily of teenager who died after
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak call for better
OL,5,Cprotection
OL,7,F"Juliette is a force in this world.
OL,8,FWith her beautifully positive energy
OL,9,Fshe spread fun, love and happiness to
OL,10,Fthose around her and she continues to
OL,11,Fdo so now.
OL,13,F"The devastation of her loss to us,
OL,14,Fher family and friends is immeasurable.
OL,16,F"Sharing stories of the empathy,
OL,17,Fwarmth and fun that she created is
OL,18,Fhelping her family and friends through
OL,19,Fat this time. Her energy continues to
OL,20,Fmake the people who love her find a
OL,21,Fway.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774054967
OL,3,CFamily of teenager who died after
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak call for better
OL,5,Cprotection
OL,7,F"The illness took her from us so
OL,8,Fquickly."
OL,10,FMr Kenny said he first became aware
OL,11,Fthat his daughter was ill when she
OL,12,Fvomited in the early hours of Friday
OL,13,FMarch 13.
OL,15,FJuliette, a year 13 student at Queen
OL,16,FElizabeth's Grammar School in
OL,17,FFaversham, exhibited no other symptoms
OL,18,Fat that time, he added.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@IO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774054967
OL,3,CFamily of teenager who died after
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak call for better
OL,5,Cprotection
OL,7,F"In the morning on Friday, she was
OL,8,Ftaken, by us, to our local emergency
OL,9,Fdrop-in as a discolouration appeared
OL,10,Fon her cheeks," Mr Kenny said.
OL,12,F"She was given antibiotics and sent by
OL,13,Fambulance to A&E.
OL,15,F"Juliette fought bravely for hours,
OL,16,Fbut despite the fantastic NHS hospital
OL,17,Fstaff fighting alongside her,
OL,18,Fmeningitis took her from us less than
OL,19,F12 hours later.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@OO]tD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774054967
OL,3,CFamily of teenager who died after
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak call for better
OL,5,Cprotection
OL,7,F"We were with her at the end, and the
OL,8,Flast sounds that she heard were the
OL,9,Fvoices of those who loved her telling
OL,10,Fher how very much loved and cherished
OL,11,Fshe is."
OL,13,FAlong with the Meningitis Research
OL,14,FFoundation, Mr Kenny and his family
OL,15,Fare calling for the UK to take urgent
OL,16,Faction to improve access to the menB
OL,17,Fvaccination for teenagers and young
OL,18,Fpeople.
OL,20,F"No family should experience this pain
OL,21,Fand tragedy," he said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@HO]|D@AOU}D@MO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774054967
OL,3,CFamily of teenager who died after
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak call for better
OL,5,Cprotection
OL,7,F"This can be avoided. There are young
OL,8,Fpeople currently battling this and
OL,9,Fyoung people still at risk.
OL,11,F"As parents, we knew our children
OL,12,Fwould change the world and be a force
OL,13,Ffor good.
OL,15,F"The work to protect young people has
OL,16,Fstarted. It needs to be more.
OL,18,F"Juliette's impact on this world must
OL,19,Fbe lasting change. Now is the time to
OL,20,Fensure families are safe from the
OL,21,Fimpact of meningitis B."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOUzD@AOU}D@XO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774054967
OL,3,CFamily of teenager who died after
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak call for better
OL,5,Cprotection
OL,7,FVinny Smith, chief executive of
OL,8,FMeningitis Research Foundation, said
OL,9,Fin 2015 the charity's calls for the
OL,10,FmenB vaccination to be "routinely
OL,11,Favailable" on the NHS for all at-risk
OL,12,Fage groups was "not taken forward" as
OL,13,Fit was "judged not to be cost-
OL,14,Feffective".
OL,16,FThe menB jab was introduced on the NHS
OL,17,Ffor babies in 2015, meaning the
OL,18,Fmajority of young people born before
OL,19,Fthen are not protected against it
OL,20,Funless they have had the jab privately.
OL,26,@rD@XOUsD@JO]tD@POUtD@bO]uD@HOUvD@JO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774054967
OL,3,CFamily of teenager who died after
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak call for better
OL,5,Cprotection
OL,7,FThe Kenny family were not aware that
OL,8,Fthe vaccination is not routinely
OL,9,Favailable on the NHS for teenagers and
OL,10,Fyoung adults, and that to have this
OL,11,Fthey would need to pay for it
OL,12,Fprivately.
OL,14,FMr Smith called on the Government to
OL,15,F"decide now to save lives" and
OL,16,Fhighlighted menB's "lifelong impact",
OL,17,Fincluding disabilities caused by the
OL,18,Fbug.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@ZO]xD@TOUxD@dO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774054967
OL,3,CFamily of teenager who died after
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak call for better
OL,5,Cprotection
OL,7,FHe said: "When we made the case for
OL,8,FmenB vaccination to be routinely
OL,9,Favailable on the NHS in 2015 for all
OL,10,Fat-risk age groups, wider protection
OL,11,Ffor teenagers and young adults was not
OL,12,Ftaken forward (it was judged to not be
OL,13,Fcost-effective within the criteria
OL,14,Fused at the time).
OL,16,F"Our concern, then and now, is that
OL,17,Fthis has not fully reflected the
OL,18,Fimpact of menB or the full value
OL,19,Fprotection from a vaccine brings.
OL,26,@oD@JOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774054967
OL,3,CFamily of teenager who died after
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak call for better
OL,5,Cprotection
OL,7,F"It hasn't accounted for the severity
OL,8,Fof meningitis, its lifelong impact, or
OL,9,Fthe trauma and bereavement experienced
OL,10,Fby families.
OL,12,F"People across the country will have
OL,13,Fseen that impact this week; we believe
OL,14,Fthe UK Government can decide now to
OL,15,Fsave lives and limit the lifelong
OL,16,Fdisabilities caused by meningitis,
OL,17,Fprotecting people for generations to
OL,18,Fcome."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUzD@FO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774054967
OL,3,CFamily of teenager who died after
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak call for better
OL,5,Cprotection
OL,7,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,8,Fsaid that as of 5pm on Wednesday, 15
OL,9,Fcases of meningitis have been
OL,10,Fconfirmed and a further 12 are under
OL,11,Finvestigation.
OL,13,FThis takes the total to 27 cases of
OL,14,Feither confirmed or suspected
OL,15,Fmeningitis, up from 20 on Wednesday.
OL,17,FCurrently, nine of the 15 confirmed
OL,18,Fcases are known to be caused by menB.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774054967
OL,3,CFamily of teenager who died after
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak call for better
OL,5,Cprotection
OL,7,FOn Thursday, 40 MPs signed a letter
OL,8,Faddressed to the Health Secretary
OL,9,Fcalling on the Government and health
OL,10,Fofficials to work with universities
OL,11,Facross the country on catch-up
OL,12,Fvaccination programmes, and to improve
OL,13,Fawareness.
OL,15,FIt also said the joint committee on
OL,16,Fvaccination and immunisation (JCVI)
OL,17,Freview of eligibility for meningitis
OL,18,Fvaccines should be conducted at pace.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G14/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41615
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774054967
OL,3,CFamily of teenager who died after
OL,4,Cmeningitis outbreak call for better
OL,5,Cprotection
OL,7,FAs of Thursday, the vaccine programme
OL,8,Fin Kent has been rolled out to anyone
OL,9,Fwho attended the Club Chemistry venue
OL,10,Ffrom March 5 to March 15, year 12 and
OL,11,F13 pupils at affected schools,
OL,12,Fstudents and staff at the University
OL,13,Fof Kent and Canterbury Christ Church
OL,14,Funiversity, and close contacts of
OL,15,Fconfirmed or suspected cases.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G15/16
